<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>SecureTheCloud | Zero-Trust Runtime for AI Agents</title>
  <meta
    name="description"
    content="SecureTheCloud is the zero-trust runtime for AI agents, combining deterministic authorization, real-time risk evaluation, and cryptographically verifiable enforcement."
  />
  <meta name="theme-color" content="#07101d" />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #07101d;
      --bg-elev: #0b1730;
      --bg-elev-2: #0f1e3d;
      --panel: rgba(16, 29, 58, 0.72);
      --panel-strong: rgba(12, 24, 49, 0.9);
      --text: #f4f7fb;
      --muted: #a8b4c8;
      --muted-2: #7f8ca2;
      --line: rgba(129, 156, 209, 0.18);
      --line-strong: rgba(129, 156, 209, 0.28);
      --gold: #d6b04d;
      --gold-2: #f2cf73;
      --blue: #67b8ff;
      --blue-2: #39d2ff;
      --success: #38d27d;
      --danger: #ff7373;
      --shadow: 0 18px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.32);
      --radius-xl: 28px;
      --radius-lg: 22px;
      --radius-md: 16px;
      --radius-sm: 12px;
      --container: 1220px;
      --header-h: 82px;
    }

    * { box-sizing: border-box; }
    html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Inter, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.09), transparent 32%),
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(57, 210, 255, 0.12), transparent 26%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, #050b15 0%, #07101d 26%, #081225 100%);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    body::before {
      content: "";
      position: fixed;
      inset: 0;
      pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(89, 120, 170, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(89, 120, 170, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 38px 38px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.55), transparent 84%);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
    img { max-width: 100%; display: block; }

    .container {
      width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 40px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 10px 16px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.24);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.16), rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.06));
      color: var(--gold-2);
      font-size: 0.84rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .section {
      padding: 112px 0;
      position: relative;
    }

    .section.compact { padding: 88px 0; }

    .section-title {
      margin: 0 0 16px;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3rem);
      line-height: 1.05;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }

    .section-intro {
      max-width: 760px;
      margin: 0 0 42px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }

    .card {
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(18, 31, 63, 0.86), rgba(10, 19, 38, 0.9));
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      transition: transform 0.28s ease, border-color 0.28s ease, box-shadow 0.28s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .card::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background:
        linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(214,176,77,0.06), transparent 35%),
        linear-gradient(240deg, rgba(57,210,255,0.07), transparent 38%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      border-color: rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.26);
      box-shadow: 0 22px 68px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.36);
    }

    .card-inner {
      position: relative;
      padding: 30px;
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .muted {
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .btn-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      min-height: 52px;
      padding: 0 22px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
      background: rgba(13, 25, 49, 0.7);
      color: var(--text);
      font-weight: 700;
      transition: transform 0.22s ease, border-color 0.22s ease, background 0.22s ease, box-shadow 0.22s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
    }

    .btn:hover,
    .btn:focus-visible {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      border-color: rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.34);
      background: rgba(18, 33, 64, 0.92);
      outline: none;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      border-color: rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.38);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(214,176,77,0.24), rgba(214,176,77,0.13));
      color: #fff4d0;
    }

    .btn-primary:hover,
    .btn-primary:focus-visible {
      border-color: rgba(242, 207, 115, 0.55);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(214,176,77,0.34), rgba(214,176,77,0.18));
    }

    .btn-link {
      padding: 0;
      min-height: auto;
      border: 0;
      background: transparent;
      box-shadow: none;
      color: var(--blue);
    }

    .btn-link:hover,
    .btn-link:focus-visible {
      transform: none;
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--blue-2);
    }

    .site-header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 1000;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: rgba(4, 9, 17, 0.7);
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(129, 156, 209, 0.12);
    }

    .site-header-inner {
      min-height: var(--header-h);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .brand {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .brand-mark {
      width: 48px;
      height: 48px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: #f6dd96;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.32);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(214,176,77,0.16), rgba(214,176,77,0.05));
      box-shadow: inset 0 1px 0 rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
    }

    .nav {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 28px;
      flex: 1;
      justify-content: center;
    }

    .nav a {
      color: #dce4f2;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      transition: color 0.2s ease;
    }

    .nav a:hover,
    .nav a:focus-visible {
      color: #ffffff;
      outline: none;
    }

    .header-actions {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      flex-shrink: 0;
    }

    .hero {
      padding: 94px 0 58px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.98fr 1.02fr;
      gap: 48px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .hero-copy h1 {
      margin: 18px 0 18px;
      font-size: clamp(3rem, 6vw, 5.35rem);
      line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: -0.055em;
      max-width: 11ch;
    }

    .hero-copy p {
      max-width: 680px;
      margin: 0 0 28px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.15rem;
    }

    .hero-proof {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      max-width: 820px;
    }

    .hero-proof .proof-pill {
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(10, 20, 40, 0.5);
    }

    .proof-label {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.76rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.07em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted-2);
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .proof-value {
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #eef4ff;
    }

    .hero-visual {
      min-height: 620px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .hero-visual-shell {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 30px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(57,210,255,0.11), transparent 30%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(13,25,50,0.86), rgba(8,16,32,0.95));
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      padding: 28px;
    }

    .hero-visual-shell::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(rgba(80, 104, 145, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(80, 104, 145, 0.06) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 30px 30px;
      mask-image: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.9), transparent 96%);
      pointer-events: none;
    }

    .visual-head {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-bottom: 26px;
    }

    .visual-title {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .visual-subtitle {
      margin: 6px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .visual-status {
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(13, 24, 48, 0.78);
      color: #d8e3f6;
      font-weight: 700;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .graph {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
      min-height: 470px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.08);
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(6,12,24,0.2), rgba(6,12,24,0.08));
      padding: 10px;
    }

    .graph-node {
      position: absolute;
      min-width: 150px;
      max-width: 190px;
      padding: 14px 16px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.2);
      background: rgba(12, 23, 45, 0.95);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
      animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .graph-node small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted-2);
      font-size: 0.72rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .graph-node strong {
      font-size: 0.98rem;
      line-height: 1.25;
    }

    .graph-node.node-accent {
      border-color: rgba(57, 210, 255, 0.26);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 1px rgba(57,210,255,0.06), 0 12px 34px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    }

    .graph-node.node-gold {
      border-color: rgba(214, 176, 77, 0.28);
    }

    .graph-node.node-success {
      border-color: rgba(56, 210, 125, 0.28);
    }

    .graph-line {
      position: absolute;
      height: 2px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(103,184,255,0.16), rgba(103,184,255,0.75), rgba(214,176,77,0.46));
      transform-origin: left center;
      opacity: 0.9;
      animation: pulse-line 2.8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .graph-line.dashed {
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(
        90deg,
        rgba(214,176,77,0.05) 0 6px,
        rgba(214,176,77,0.82) 6px 14px
      );
      height: 3px;
    }

    .graph-dot {
      position: absolute;
      width: 12px;
      height: 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: radial-gradient(circle, #ffffff 0%, #67b8ff 36%, rgba(103,184,255,0.08) 68%, transparent 72%);
      box-shadow: 0 0 24px rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.7);
      animation: pulse-dot 1.8s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    .hero-band {
      padding-top: 18px;
    }

    .band-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .band-item {
      padding: 22px 22px 20px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(15, 27, 54, 0.84), rgba(9, 17, 34, 0.94));
      box-shadow: 0 16px 46px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.22);
    }

    .band-item strong {
      display: block;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    }

    .band-item span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .grid-3 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .grid-2 {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .feature-card h3,
    .arch-card h3,
    .capability-card h3,
    .proof-card h3,
    .company-card h3 {
      margin: 14px 0 10px;
      font-size: 1.32rem;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    }

    .feature-card p,
    .arch-card p,
    .capability-card p,
    .proof-card p,
    .company-card p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .process-strip {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(6, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 34px;
    }

    .process-step {
      position: relative;
      padding: 24px 18px 22px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(12, 22, 43, 0.78);
      min-height: 170px;
    }

    .process-step::after {
      content: "→";
      position: absolute;
      top: 50%;
      right: -14px;
      transform: translateY(-50%);
      font-size: 1.2rem;
      color: rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.7);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    .process-step:last-child::after { display: none; }

    .process-step .step-number {
      display: inline-grid;
      place-items: center;
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      background: rgba(103, 184, 255, 0.12);
      color: var(--blue);
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .process-step h3 {
      margin: 0 0 8px;
      font-size: 1.06rem;
    }

    .process-step p {
      margin: 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .scenario-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 0.98fr 1.02fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .scenario-card ul {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin: 18px 0 0;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .scenario-card li + li { margin-top: 10px; }

    .scenario-flow {
      padding: 24px;
      min-height: 100%;
    }

    .scenario-steps {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }

    .scenario-step {
      padding: 18px 20px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(11, 22, 44, 0.72);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 16px;
    }

    .scenario-step strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .scenario-step span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .scenario-step .badge {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 0.78rem;
      white-space: nowrap;
      letter-spacing: 0.06em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      border: 1px solid rgba(129,156,209,0.18);
      background: rgba(12, 24, 48, 0.85);
    }

    .proof-previews {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 24px;
    }

    .proof-preview {
      min-height: 320px;
    }

    .proof-preview .preview-shell {
      margin-top: 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(7,13,26,0.9), rgba(10,19,36,0.98));
      min-height: 190px;
      padding: 18px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .mini-bar {
      height: 10px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(57,210,255,0.28), rgba(57,210,255,0.9));
      width: var(--w, 70%);
    }

    .mini-row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .mini-cell {
      padding: 12px;
      border-radius: 14px;
      background: rgba(16, 29, 58, 0.78);
      border: 1px solid rgba(129,156,209,0.12);
      min-height: 68px;
    }

    .mini-cell strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .mini-cell small {
      color: var(--muted-2);
      font-size: 0.78rem;
    }

    .dev-layout {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
      gap: 28px;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .proof-list {
      display: grid;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .proof-item {
      display: flex;
      gap: 14px;
      align-items: flex-start;
      padding: 16px 18px;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      background: rgba(10, 20, 40, 0.58);
    }

    .proof-item .icon {
      width: 34px;
      height: 34px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      flex: 0 0 34px;
      background: rgba(56, 210, 125, 0.12);
      color: var(--success);
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .cta-band {
      padding: 42px;
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      align-items: center;
      text-align: center;
      background:
        radial-gradient(circle at left top, rgba(214,176,77,0.13), transparent 30%),
        radial-gradient(circle at right center, rgba(57,210,255,0.12), transparent 36%),
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(12,23,45,0.94), rgba(9,17,34,0.98));
    }

    .cta-band h2 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 3vw, 3.4rem);
      line-height: 1.02;
      letter-spacing: -0.04em;
    }

    .cta-band p {
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 760px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 1.08rem;
    }

    .site-footer {
      padding: 48px 0 40px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(129, 156, 209, 0.14);
      background: rgba(5, 9, 17, 0.42);
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr repeat(4, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 28px;
    }

    .footer-col h3 {
      margin: 0 0 14px;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.08em;
      color: var(--muted-2);
    }

    .footer-col a,
    .footer-col p {
      display: block;
      margin: 0 0 10px;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .footer-col a:hover,
    .footer-col a:focus-visible {
      color: #fff;
      outline: none;
    }

    .footer-brand p {
      max-width: 330px;
      color: var(--muted);
      margin-top: 14px;
    }

    .footer-bottom {
      margin-top: 26px;
      padding-top: 22px;
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(129,156,209,0.12);
      color: var(--muted-2);
      font-size: 0.94rem;
    }

    .reveal {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(26px);
      transition: opacity 0.8s ease, transform 0.8s ease;
    }

    .reveal.in {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }

    .skip-link {
      position: absolute;
      left: 12px;
      top: -44px;
      padding: 10px 14px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: #0f1e3d;
      border: 1px solid var(--line);
      color: #fff;
      z-index: 1200;
    }

    .skip-link:focus { top: 12px; }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-4px); }
    }

    @keyframes pulse-line {
      0%, 100% { opacity: 0.6; }
      50% { opacity: 1; }
    }

    @keyframes pulse-dot {
      0%, 100% { transform: scale(0.94); opacity: 0.88; }
      50% { transform: scale(1.06); opacity: 1; }
    }

    @media (max-width: 1180px) {
      .nav {
        gap: 18px;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .scenario-layout,
      .dev-layout {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-visual {
        min-height: auto;
      }

      .process-strip {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      }

      .process-step:nth-child(3)::after,
      .process-step:nth-child(6)::after {
        display: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .site-header-inner {
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        padding: 16px 0;
      }

      .nav {
        order: 3;
        width: 100%;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        overflow-x: auto;
        padding-bottom: 4px;
      }

      .proof-previews,
      .grid-3,
      .grid-2,
      .hero-proof,
      .band-grid,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .process-strip {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .process-step::after { display: none; }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 54px;
      }

      .hero-copy h1 {
        max-width: none;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 700px) {
      .container {
        width: min(var(--container), calc(100% - 24px));
      }

      .section {
        padding: 86px 0;
      }

      .hero-proof .proof-pill,
      .card-inner,
      .cta-band {
        padding: 22px;
      }

      .btn-row {
        align-items: stretch;
      }

      .btn {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .header-actions {
        width: 100%;
      }

      .header-actions .btn {
        flex: 1;
      }

      .graph {
        min-height: 520px;
      }

      .graph-node {
        min-width: 130px;
        max-width: 170px;
        padding: 12px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <a class="skip-link" href="#main">Skip to content</a>

  <header class="site-header" aria-label="Primary">
    <div class="container site-header-inner">
      <a class="brand" href="/">
        <span class="brand-mark" aria-hidden="true">STC</span>
        <span>SecureTheCloud</span>
      </a>

      <nav class="nav" aria-label="Main navigation">
        <a href="#platform">Platform</a>
        <a href="#architecture">Architecture</a>
        <a href="#use-cases">Use Cases</a>
        <a href="#developers">Developers</a>
        <a href="#company">Company</a>
      </nav>

      <div class="header-actions">
        <a class="btn" href="https://app.securethecloud.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Console</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/request-demo/">Request Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main id="main">
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div class="hero-copy reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">SecureTheCloud</span>
          <h1>Zero-Trust Runtime for AI Agents</h1>
          <p>
            Deterministic authorization, real-time risk evaluation, and cryptographically verifiable
            enforcement for agentic systems.
          </p>

          <div class="btn-row" aria-label="Hero calls to action">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/request-demo/">Request Demo</a>
            <a class="btn" href="#architecture">View Architecture</a>
            <a class="btn btn-link" href="https://app.securethecloud.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Console</a>
          </div>

          <div class="hero-proof" aria-label="Platform proof points">
            <div class="proof-pill">
              <span class="proof-label">Promise</span>
              <span class="proof-value">Deterministic authorization</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-pill">
              <span class="proof-label">Runtime</span>
              <span class="proof-value">Scoped execution boundaries</span>
            </div>
            <div class="proof-pill">
              <span class="proof-label">Audit</span>
              <span class="proof-value">Cryptographic decision lineage</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-visual reveal" aria-hidden="true">
          <div class="hero-visual-shell">
            <div class="visual-head">
              <div>
                <h2 class="visual-title">Runtime Authorization Graph</h2>
                <p class="visual-subtitle">Deterministic evaluation flowing across policy, risk, and enforcement.</p>
              </div>
              <div class="visual-status">Runtime active</div>
            </div>

            <div class="graph">
              <div class="graph-node node-accent" style="left: 18px; top: 48px;">
                <small>Request</small>
                <strong>Agent action initiated</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-gold" style="left: 256px; top: 20px; animation-delay: .2s;">
                <small>RiskDNA</small>
                <strong>Contextual runtime scoring</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-accent" style="left: 252px; top: 172px; animation-delay: .5s;">
                <small>Policy</small>
                <strong>Deterministic decision evaluation</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-success" style="left: 500px; top: 42px; animation-delay: .8s;">
                <small>Authorization</small>
                <strong>Scoped token issuance</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-gold" style="left: 496px; top: 208px; animation-delay: .4s;">
                <small>Enforcement</small>
                <strong>Runtime boundary application</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-accent" style="left: 646px; top: 86px; animation-delay: .7s;">
                <small>Session governance</small>
                <strong>Introspection, revocation, audit</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-node node-gold" style="left: 650px; top: 274px; animation-delay: .9s;">
                <small>Operator visibility</small>
                <strong>Control plane and executive proof</strong>
              </div>

              <div class="graph-line" style="left: 154px; top: 97px; width: 130px; transform: rotate(-16deg);"></div>
              <div class="graph-line" style="left: 154px; top: 109px; width: 136px; transform: rotate(18deg);"></div>
              <div class="graph-line" style="left: 424px; top: 90px; width: 92px; transform: rotate(10deg);"></div>
              <div class="graph-line" style="left: 425px; top: 246px; width: 95px; transform: rotate(-8deg);"></div>
              <div class="graph-line dashed" style="left: 584px; top: 116px; width: 92px; transform: rotate(6deg);"></div>
              <div class="graph-line dashed" style="left: 592px; top: 248px; width: 102px; transform: rotate(16deg);"></div>

              <div class="graph-dot" style="left: 282px; top: 74px;"></div>
              <div class="graph-dot" style="left: 281px; top: 216px; animation-delay: .6s;"></div>
              <div class="graph-dot" style="left: 515px; top: 102px; animation-delay: .2s;"></div>
              <div class="graph-dot" style="left: 515px; top: 246px; animation-delay: .4s;"></div>
              <div class="graph-dot" style="left: 658px; top: 132px; animation-delay: .8s;"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact hero-band">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="band-grid">
          <div class="band-item">
            <strong>Govern agent actions before execution</strong>
            <span>Runtime policy acts before privileged work spreads across systems.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="band-item">
            <strong>Constrain blast radius in live context</strong>
            <span>Access remains bounded by RiskDNA, scope, and runtime policy.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="band-item">
            <strong>Preserve decision lineage end to end</strong>
            <span>Every authorization carries traceable proof tied to its evaluation.</span>
          </div>
          <div class="band-item">
            <strong>Keep operators and executives aligned</strong>
            <span>One runtime connects control, evidence, and explanation without drift.</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact" id="platform">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal">
          <h2 class="section-title">AI agents need runtime control, not just static policy</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            AI systems can issue requests, chain actions, and operate across sensitive environments faster than
            traditional controls can safely govern. SecureTheCloud enforces decisions at runtime, before the action executes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card feature-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Problem 01</span>
              <h3>Identity alone is not enough</h3>
              <p>
                Knowing who initiated a request does not explain whether the action is safe in its current operational context.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card feature-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Problem 02</span>
              <h3>Post-incident detection is too late</h3>
              <p>
                Security teams need enforcement before execution, not only visibility after damage has already occurred.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card feature-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Problem 03</span>
              <h3>Agent behavior must stay governable</h3>
              <p>
                Runtime actions require deterministic policy, traceable decisions, and bounded blast radius at the moment of execution.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="architecture">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Architecture</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">One runtime. Three planes. Deterministic control.</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            SecureTheCloud separates intelligence, enforcement, and governance so AI-driven actions can be evaluated,
            authorized, and contained in real time.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card arch-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Decision Plane</span>
              <h3>Risk and policy evaluation</h3>
              <p>
                Computes RiskDNA, evaluates intent against deterministic policy, and produces a verifiable authorization outcome.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card arch-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Enforcement Plane</span>
              <h3>Runtime control and session governance</h3>
              <p>
                Issues scoped tokens, validates sessions, enforces revocation, and constrains access at execution time.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card arch-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Control Plane</span>
              <h3>Visibility, audit, and operational oversight</h3>
              <p>
                Provides runtime state, blast radius views, policy revision tracking, and executive observability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-row reveal" style="margin-top: 28px;">
          <a class="btn" href="/shield/">Learn through Shield</a>
          <a class="btn" href="/riskdna/">View RiskDNA</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">How it works</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">How SecureTheCloud works</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            Every authorization event carries verifiable decision context tied to the evaluation that approved it.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-strip">
          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Agent Request</h3>
            <p>An agent attempts an action across a governed execution surface.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>RiskDNA Evaluation</h3>
            <p>Signals are scored in runtime context before any privileged action proceeds.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>Policy Decision</h3>
            <p>Intent is checked against deterministic authorization policy and threshold logic.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h3>Scoped Authorization</h3>
            <p>A bounded token is issued only when policy and context allow the request.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">5</div>
            <h3>Runtime Enforcement</h3>
            <p>Execution proceeds within constrained blast-radius and tenant-safe boundaries.</p>
          </article>

          <article class="process-step reveal">
            <div class="step-number">6</div>
            <h3>Session Governance</h3>
            <p>Introspection, revocation, and audit remain active throughout the lifecycle.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="capabilities">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Core capabilities</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">One platform. Three governing surfaces.</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            Shield, RiskDNA, and Copilot operate as integrated capabilities under the SecureTheCloud runtime.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card capability-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Shield</span>
              <h3>Contain and visualize blast radius</h3>
              <p>
                Maps identity paths, privileged relationships, and enforcement boundaries to reduce operational exposure.
              </p>
              <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 22px;">
                <a class="btn" href="/shield/">Learn about Shield</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card capability-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">RiskDNA</span>
              <h3>Deterministic runtime scoring</h3>
              <p>
                Scores requests using governed signals and operational context before the action is allowed.
              </p>
              <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 22px;">
                <a class="btn" href="/riskdna/">Learn about RiskDNA</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card capability-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Copilot</span>
              <h3>Governed explanations grounded in platform truth</h3>
              <p>
                Explains what happened, why it mattered, and what to do next without mutating system state.
              </p>
              <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 22px;">
                <a class="btn" href="/copilot/">Learn about Copilot</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact" id="use-cases">
      <div class="container scenario-layout">
        <article class="card scenario-card reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="eyebrow">Use-case spotlight</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.8vw, 3rem); margin-top: 18px;">
              See the runtime respond to a real operation
            </h2>
            <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom: 0; max-width: 100%;">
              <strong>After-hours refund attempt from a new device.</strong> SecureTheCloud recomputes risk, evaluates
              the action against runtime policy, constrains blast radius, and preserves decision lineage for operators and executives.
            </p>

            <ul>
              <li>Request arrives outside normal operating hours</li>
              <li>Runtime context increases RiskDNA score</li>
              <li>Deterministic policy evaluates intent and boundary conditions</li>
              <li>Scoped access is applied before execution proceeds</li>
            </ul>

            <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 22px;">
              <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/aegis-air/">Explore Use Cases</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card scenario-flow reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="eyebrow">Scenario flow</span>
            <div class="scenario-steps">
              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Request detected</strong>
                  <span>New device and after-hours context captured at runtime.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Signal</span>
              </div>

              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Risk increases</strong>
                  <span>RiskDNA recomputes the operation against live context.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">RiskDNA</span>
              </div>

              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Policy evaluated</strong>
                  <span>Intent is checked against deterministic authorization rules.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Policy</span>
              </div>

              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Access bounded</strong>
                  <span>Execution receives scoped authorization and constrained blast radius.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Enforcement</span>
              </div>

              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Session governed</strong>
                  <span>Session remains subject to introspection, revocation, and audit.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Session</span>
              </div>

              <div class="scenario-step">
                <div>
                  <strong>Executive brief generated</strong>
                  <span>Governed summary explains what happened and why it matters.</span>
                </div>
                <span class="badge">Copilot</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section" id="proof">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="eyebrow">Product proof</span>
          <h2 class="section-title">Built for operators. Designed for governed execution.</h2>
          <p class="section-intro">
            SecureTheCloud exposes runtime state, blast-radius context, and executive explanation without collapsing the marketing site into an operator console.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="proof-previews">
          <article class="card proof-card proof-preview reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Preview 01</span>
              <h3>Runtime Command Center</h3>
              <p>Track decisions, sessions, policy revision, and runtime health from the control plane.</p>
              <div class="preview-shell" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="mini-row">
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Audit</strong><small>Integrity verified</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Sessions</strong><small>Live runtime state</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Policy</strong><small>Versioned evaluation</small></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-bar" style="--w: 88%;"></div>
                <div class="mini-bar" style="--w: 72%;"></div>
                <div class="mini-row">
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Decisions</strong><small>Runtime stream</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Risk</strong><small>Bounded by policy</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Actions</strong><small>Governed visibility</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card proof-card proof-preview reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Preview 02</span>
              <h3>Blast Radius and RiskDNA</h3>
              <p>Understand downstream impact, context propagation, and resource exposure before actions execute.</p>
              <div class="preview-shell" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="mini-row">
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Tenant</strong><small>Runtime scope</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Intent</strong><small>Authorized action</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Risk</strong><small>Context score</small></div>
                </div>
                <div class="mini-bar" style="--w: 94%;"></div>
                <div class="mini-row">
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>payment_db</strong><small>Protected resource</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>audit_ledger</strong><small>Blast-radius path</small></div>
                  <div class="mini-cell"><strong>backup</strong><small>Scoped dependency</small></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card proof-card proof-preview reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Preview 03</span>
              <h3>Executive Decision Briefing</h3>
              <p>Translate governed platform signals into concise operational explanation and next-step guidance.</p>
              <div class="preview-shell" aria-hidden="true">
                <div class="mini-cell"><strong>What happened</strong><small>After-hours refund operation detected</small></div>
                <div class="mini-cell"><strong>Why it mattered</strong><small>Risk increased due to runtime context</small></div>
                <div class="mini-cell"><strong>What changed</strong><small>Access was bounded by deterministic policy</small></div>
                <div class="mini-bar" style="--w: 61%;"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>

        <div class="btn-row reveal" style="margin-top: 28px;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="https://app.securethecloud.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Console</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact" id="developers">
      <div class="container dev-layout">
        <article class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="eyebrow">Developers</span>
            <h2 class="section-title" style="font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 2.8vw, 3rem); margin-top: 18px;">
              Built for runtime enforcement, not static policy alone
            </h2>
            <p class="section-intro" style="margin-bottom: 0; max-width: 100%;">
              SecureTheCloud is designed for organizations building or operating agentic systems that need
              verifiable authorization, live revocation, scoped execution, and deterministic auditability.
            </p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="card reveal">
          <div class="card-inner">
            <span class="eyebrow">Developer proof</span>
            <div class="proof-list">
              <div class="proof-item">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Runtime policy evaluation</strong>
                  <div class="muted">Decisions are produced in context at execution time, not after the fact.</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="proof-item">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Session introspection and revocation</strong>
                  <div class="muted">Issued authorization remains governable throughout the session lifecycle.</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="proof-item">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Tenant-aware enforcement</strong>
                  <div class="muted">Runtime state stays bounded by tenant isolation and scoped access rules.</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="proof-item">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Audit-ready decision lineage</strong>
                  <div class="muted">Every authorization event remains traceable back to its governing evaluation context.</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="proof-item">
                <div class="icon">✓</div>
                <div>
                  <strong>Governed integration with platform signals</strong>
                  <div class="muted">RiskDNA, policy, and control-plane surfaces remain aligned and verifiable.</div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>

            <div class="btn-row" style="margin-top: 24px;">
              <a class="btn" href="/labs/">Developers</a>
              <a class="btn btn-link" href="https://app.securethecloud.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Open Console</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section compact" id="company">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="grid-3">
          <article class="card company-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Company</span>
              <h3>Deterministic by design</h3>
              <p>
                SecureTheCloud is built around runtime control, governed decisioning, and operational traceability.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card company-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Enterprise</span>
              <h3>Designed for operational trust</h3>
              <p>
                The platform aligns security controls, executive visibility, and product architecture into one runtime layer.
              </p>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="card company-card reveal">
            <div class="card-inner">
              <span class="eyebrow">Contact</span>
              <h3>Engage the platform team</h3>
