    <section class="section compact">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="card cta-band reveal">
          <h2>Bring deterministic control to AI agent runtime</h2>
          <p>
            SecureTheCloud gives security teams a governed runtime layer for agentic actions across policy, enforcement, and operational visibility.
          </p>
          <div class="btn-row" style="justify-content: center;">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="/request-demo/">Request Demo</a>
